HEADWORD: Allayment
<hw>Al*lay"ment</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An allaying;
that which allays; mitigation.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The like <qex>allayment</qex> could I give my grief.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>all-devouring</ent>⟦br⟧
